"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-28-convicted-rapist-booed-first-olympics-beach-volleyball\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - Fans booed a Dutch beach volleyball player convicted of raping an underaged girl as he played his first match at the Paris Olympics, where his controversial selection has put the sport in the spotlight.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9927008424371317, \"rank\": 0.005398036242192255, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"a Dutch beach volleyball player\", \"from\": 33, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"an underaged girl\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 102}, {\"ngram\": \"his first match\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 131}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 153}, {\"ngram\": \"his controversial selection\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 188}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steven van der Velde, now aged 29, was convicted in 2016 of raping an underage girl and sentenced to four years in prison.\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Steven van der Velde\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"an underage girl\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He walked onto centre court Sunday with teammate Matthew Immers on Sunday morning to cheers and applause, with many orange-clad Dutch fans standing to clap the pair.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"centre court\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"teammate Matthew Immers\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday morning\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"cheers\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"applause\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"many orange-clad Dutch fans\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he was introduced individually over the loudspeaker, however, there was a loud chorus of boos from the crowd.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the loudspeaker\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"a loud chorus\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"boos\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were also sporadic boos as he served throughout the game.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sporadic boos\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The player has won the backing of his country's national Olympic committee, and exchanged a warm hug with teammate Immers before the start of the game.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The player\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"the backing\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"his country's national Olympic committee\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"a warm hug\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"teammate Immers\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But his selection has drawn outrage among women's and sports safety groups.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his selection\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"outrage\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"women's and sports safety groups\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials said the player would be separated from his teammates, not stay in the athletes' village, and forbidden from speaking to media.\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Officials\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"the player\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"his teammates\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His teammate Immers told reporters after the match that they had been \\\"disappointed\\\" by all the focus on van der Velde's past conviction, particularly after a \\\"hard fight\\\" to qualify.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His teammate Immers\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"all the focus\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"van der Velde's past conviction\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"hard fight\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know the guy for two, three years together and we played every tournament,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the guy\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"every tournament\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What is in the past is in the past, and he had his punishment.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"his punishment\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me that's a big example that you grew, you learned a lot from it.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big example\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What happened in the past\\u2026 it's not good of course.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But right now we are trying to enjoy and go to the next round.\\\"\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next round\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ju'Riese Colon, chief executive of the US-based Center for SafeSport, said she was \\\"deeply concerned that anyone convicted of sexually assaulting a minor could participate\\\" in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ju'Riese Colon\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"chief executive\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the US-based Center\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"SafeSport\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With teams from around the world convening in Paris, many of which include minor athletes, this sends a dangerous message that medals and money mean more than their safety,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999987109277, \"rank\": 1.2890734376580862e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.